    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165470/extras/f4f95e1e1f1a9c7c36ca35efe49fe4e0.avif?t=1764844155\" width=600 height=88 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165470/extras/1484d75900cb96956d4ea61b9219f023.poster.avif?t=1764844155\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165470/extras/1484d75900cb96956d4ea61b9219f023.webm?t=1764844155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165470/extras/1484d75900cb96956d4ea61b9219f023.mp4?t=1764844155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备好迎接波浪之下充满宝藏的冒险吧！合并金币和宝石，发现超越想象的财富！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索改变游戏方式的地图，每一张都有独特的形状和背景。你能掌握所有地图并合并出最伟大的宝藏吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165470/extras/e3c6979b296e78838cf043b8f3232c46.avif?t=1764844155\" width=600 height=88 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165470/extras/b2c637961171afc9291bbbaaebf0517d.poster.avif?t=1764844155\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165470/extras/b2c637961171afc9291bbbaaebf0517d.webm?t=1764844155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165470/extras/b2c637961171afc9291bbbaaebf0517d.mp4?t=1764844155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作模式（CO-OP）</strong><br>在同一个圆顶中进行本地合作游戏，与队友一起收集积分！合并宝藏、获取强化道具，并肩冲击最高分！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>对战模式（VERSUS）</strong><br>与朋友进行本地对战！圆顶被分为两半——一边属于你，另一边属于对手。如果一名玩家的圆顶装得太满、物品溢出，另一名玩家将只有几秒钟时间尽可能多地得分，直至游戏结束！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>捕捉漂浮到水面的强力道具，并在需要时使用它们：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >炸弹：爆炸并将一切推开</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >珍珠：可与任意宝藏合并</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >红宝石诅咒：让宝藏更有价值</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爆发：摧毁所有石头</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幽灵：让宝藏穿过障碍</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 在线排行榜，展示你的高分！<br>• 合作模式，可一起游戏与合并！<br>• 对战模式，可挑战好友！<br>• 2 张独特形状的地图！<br>• 5 种激动人心的强化道具，随时改变局势！<br>• 名称和角色可完全自定义<br>• 多种角色皮肤——从海底到太空！<br>• 明亮耀眼的水下视觉风格！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游向顶端，称霸排行榜！</strong></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 乌克兰语",
